sky.f1.uk.title: WDC 2026: The Story So Far
sky.f1.uk.description: The 2024 European champion Ritchie Edhouse steps up to the oche on the afternoon of day four to face Jonny Tata, while former Masters winner Joe Cullen opens against Bradley Brooks. (14.12)

sky.f1.uk.title: WDC 2026: The Story So Far

sky.f1.uk.title: WDC 2026: The Story So Far

sky.f1.uk.title: PDC Classics 2023

sky.f1.uk.title: Taylor v Wright 2017

sky.f1.uk.title: WDC 2026: The Story So Far
sky.f1.uk.description: Former World Darts Championship semi-finalists Chris Dobey and Scott Williams compete during day six's afternoon session, facing Xiaochen Zong and Paolo Nebrida respectively. (16.12)

sky.f1.uk.title: WDC 2026: The Story So Far
sky.f1.uk.description: Gerwyn Price headlines a blockbuster day six evening line-up against Adam Gawlas. Danny Noppert meets fellow Dutchman Jurjen van der Velde as Jose de Sousa plays Ricardo Pietreczko. (16.12)

sky.f1.uk.title: WDC 2026: The Story So Far

sky.f1.uk.title: WDC 2026: The Story So Far
sky.f1.uk.description: Former World Grand Prix winner Mike De Decker plays debutant David Munyua, the first Kenyan to compete here, during the afternoon of day eight. Callan Rydz meets Patrik Kovacs. (18.12)

sky.f1.uk.title: WDC 2026: The Story So Far

sky.f1.uk.title: WDC 2026: The Story So Far

sky.f1.uk.title: WDC 2026: The Story So Far

sky.mix.uk.title: ATP/WTA Tour Classic Matches

UAndYesterday.uk.description: The Desert: Laurence Olivier narrates this exhaustive account of World War II. In the deserts of North Africa, the 8th Army battles against Rommel's Afrika Korps. S1 Ep8
